AutoCloseable, CallableStatement, PreparedStatement, Statement, Wrapper
public class AutoCloseCallableStatement
extends DelegatingCallableStatement<CallableStatement>
implements AutoCloseable, CallableStatement

An AutoCloseable CallableStatement. When the automatic resource management block construct invokes close(), close() will be called on the underlying CallableStatement.
